name: "GATES of DAWN" - Nocturne #1
description:
[Sound On]

The first of NINE NOCTURNES by HP LoveBux

Read this poem aloud while you listen...

"light-fingers grasp 
the shining gates 
to welcome in
the end 
of night"

Digital Painting Music and Poetry 
by HPL

Edition 1/1

Feel free to share your reading of this poem.
Add more sections to the poem or the music,
